                        <path d="M5 12v6c0 1.7 3.1 3 7 3s7-1.3 7-3v-6" />
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Entity Framework Core</strong>
                    <span class="about-list-copy">Budgets, allocations, and expense history</span>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="about-stack-list__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H7a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
                        <circle cx="10" cy="7" r="3.5" />
                        <path d="M19 8v6M22 11h-6" />
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                    <strong>ASP.NET Identity</strong>
                    <span class="about-list-copy">Registration, sign-in, profile, and security</span>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="about-stack-list__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="2" />
                        <path d="m4 7 8 6 8-6" />
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Account email</strong>
                    <span class="about-list-copy">Confirmation and password reset over SMTP</span>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="form-panel about-panel about-section about-developer" aria-labelledby="about-developer-title">
        <p class="about-developer__label">Developer</p>
        <h2 class="about-section-title" id="about-developer-title">Andrei James S. Alejandro</h2>
        <p class="about-body mb-0">
            Andrei James S. Alejandro designed and built SpendiTrack as a practical personal finance tool,
            focused on monthly planning, clear budgets, and a tracker that stays usable on both desktop and mobile.
            The goal is simple: help people see their spending early enough to stay in control.
        </p>
    </section>
</div>
